[SHORT DESC]
Lowers foe's accuracy 1 stage.

[LONG DESC]
<p>Lowers target's accuracy one stage.</p>
<h2>Related Moves</h2>
<p><a href="/rs/moves/flash">Flash</a> is a Normal-type equivalent, but with less accuracy.<br/ >
<a href="/rs/moves/sand-attack">Sand-Attack</a> is a Ground-type equivalent.<br/ >
<a href="/rs/moves/smokescreen">Smokescreen</a> is a Normal-type equivalent, but with more accuracy.</p>